name: toilets-app-mamuna-s-team-new
description: ## Form to submit a toilet ### Form fields * City (select) `city` * Street (text) `street` * House Nr. (text) `streetnr` * Name of location (text) `name` * Features   * Mirror (checkbox) `feat-mirror`   * Paper towels (checkbox) `feat-papertowels`   * Perfume (checkbox) `feat-perfume`   * Accessibility (text) `feat-access`   * Soap (checkbox) `feat-soap` * Number of stalls (number) `stalls` * Rating (1 - 5 toilet seats) (radio group) `rating` (Number)
